description:
Umphrey's McGee
November 8th, 2014
Madison, WI @ The Orpheum - 2000th Show! 
TourGigs HD Live Stream Rip 1080p


Source:

1080p streaming TourGigs concert > HDMI video output with composite RCA audio > Game Capture HD > MP4 > HandBrake 0.9.9.5530 (cropping and compression) > M4V  

Notes:

This is a high quality 1080p rip of UM's 2000th show as streamed on TourGigs on November 8th, 2014.  Taken from the replay, which did not have any buffering issues.  Audio and video is almost perfect for the most part (there are a couple of occasions when buffering happens, but it's only for a split second).  

Setlist:

SET 1   All in Time > The Linear -> Walk the Proud Land, Uncommon, Hurt Bird Bath, Similar Skin*, All Things Ninja**, August -> The Other Side of Things^ > August

SET 2   Mulche's Odyssey > Kimble, Where is My Mind?^^, 40's Theme, Front Porch, 1,000 Places to See Before You Die# > Bad Friday#, Slacker > G-Song^ > Slacker

ENCORE   It's About That Time# > All in Time


*w/ Muffburger Sandwich teases
**w/ Jake on drums
^one verse
